HISTORY
=======

Usage: history              - Last 20 messages from all channels
       history [N]          - Last N messages from all channels
       history [channel]    - Last 20 messages from specific channel
       history [channel] N  - Last N messages from specific channel

View recent chat history. Useful for catching up on messages you missed
while offline or away. Arguments can be in any order.

Examples:
  history           - View all recent chat
  history 50        - View last 50 messages
  history chat      - View only global chat
  history ooc 30    - View last 30 OOC messages
  history 30 ooc    - Same as above (order doesn't matter)

Maximum: 100 messages per query.

Alternative: Each channel command also has history, e.g., 'chat history 50'

See also: chat, ooc, channels
